name: r-tidymodels
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tidymodels
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tidymodels_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tidymodels/tidymodels_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e37baa004cc44389a4408137b403903007a064a147f473f44f81c1caffc10dff

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-broom >=0.7.6
    - r-cli >=2.4.0
    - r-conflicted >=1.0.4
    - r-dials >=0.0.9
    - r-dplyr >=1.0.5
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.3.3
    - r-infer >=0.5.4
    - r-modeldata >=0.1.0
    - r-parsnip >=0.1.5
    - r-purrr >=0.3.4
    - r-recipes >=0.1.16
    - r-rlang >=0.4.10
    - r-rsample >=0.0.9
    - r-rstudioapi >=0.13
    - r-tibble >=3.1.0
    - r-tidyr >=1.1.3
    - r-tune >=0.1.3
    - r-workflows >=0.2.2
    - r-workflowsets >=0.0.2
    - r-yardstick >=0.0.8
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-broom >=0.7.6
    - r-cli >=2.4.0
    - r-conflicted >=1.0.4
    - r-dials >=0.0.9
    - r-dplyr >=1.0.5
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.3.3
    - r-infer >=0.5.4
    - r-modeldata >=0.1.0
    - r-parsnip >=0.1.5
    - r-purrr >=0.3.4
    - r-recipes >=0.1.16
    - r-rlang >=0.4.10
    - r-rsample >=0.0.9
    - r-rstudioapi >=0.13
    - r-tibble >=3.1.0
    - r-tidyr >=1.1.3
    - r-tune >=0.1.3
    - r-workflows >=0.2.2
    - r-workflowsets >=0.0.2
    - r-yardstick >=0.0.8

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tidymodels')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tidymodels')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/tidymodels/tidymodels
  license: MIT
  summary: The tidy modeling "verse" is a collection of packages for  modeling and statistical analysis that share the underlying design philosophy, grammar, and data structures of the tidyverse.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - philip-khor
